      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1's belong to (low -- mid-1) group i.e. left\nso, we'll increment mid++ so it sticks to the unsorted\narray group, which means, the mid-1 absorbs that new 1\ninto it's 1's group",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1's belong to (low -- mid-1) group i.e. left\nso, we'll increment mid++ so it sticks to the unsorted array group, which means, the mid-1 absorbs that new 1 into it's 1's group",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
