      "text": "mid = 2, and 2 belongs to the extreme right, so we'll\nswap(nums[mid], nums[high])",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "mid = 2, and 2 belongs to the extreme right, so we'll swap(nums[mid], nums[high])",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RD1wXgFgDfxW1YCVzUnng",
